# Local identifier denylist for .githooks/pre-commit.
# Copy to `.secrets-denylist` (gitignored) and list YOUR real deployment
# identifiers, one POSIX extended-regex per line. Any staged change that
# introduces a match is refused, so real vault ids / hostnames / device
# names / private note paths can never reach a commit.
#
# Format examples (illustrative regexes — replace with your real values):
#   my-vault-id
#   my-host\.internal
#   MyLaptopHostname
#   PrivateTopFolder/
